<h3 class="h3">The CPA exam</h3>

<p class="mb-8">
  Messiah University gives you an edge as you prepare to take the four parts of the Certified Public
  Accounting (CPA) exam. Our students have historically exceeded the national average pass rate for
  first-time test takers. They also typically complete the exam years earlier than their peers from
  other institutions. Our alumni rave about Messiah’s Accounting program and the advantage they
  received in starting their career as a CPA.
</p>

